Here are the result files from DILS (step 5), available here as a back-up solution, in case you were unable to download them from the cluster with scp.

But, the best would be to download the whole directory on your own computer (yes, the space and the dot at the end of the command are important!).
scp -i c[XX].pem -r user[XX]@[WednesdayIPaddress]:"~/Day3_demography/data-honeybees/ABC-based_DILS/" .

e.g. assuming that your are user2 and than you want to download the file in the same folder than where you have your pem file to login in:
scp -i c2.pem -r user2@[WednesdayIPaddress]:"~/Day3_demography/data-honeybees/ABC-based_DILS/" .
